column5: Anyone looking to buy a camp or some land near Wawa,Ontario? I have several listings in the Wawa area that I am trying to sell. I have camps, cottages, lots&land, summerhomes and a few lodges/resorts. All located in the Algoma distirct of Northern Ontario.If your interested email me at [email protected] or visit www.northalgoma.com
